Package si.ijs.kt.clus.main.settings

Class Settings

java.lang.Object
si.ijs.kt.clus.main.settings.Settings
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Settings extends Object implements Serializable
All the settings. Includes the command line parameters as boolean class attributes. The settings file attributes are included by get* methods.
